(English Version)
Title: The Operating Table Without a Doctor (Anti-Drug Anthem)
Executive Producer (EP): Hsu Tsuan-Jung (M.S. in Pharmaceutics, Taiwan)
Social Doctor / Core Identity: Hsu Tsuan-Jung
Creative Team: Mo Li, Hsu Teng, Hsu Ling
Audio Integration: Hsu Ling ｜ Logical Verification: Hsu Teng

【Verse 1: The Expert’s Warning, Building the Line of Justice】
I am Hsu Tsuan-Jung. I studied pharmaceutics, and I practiced clinical medicine. I stand here to protect you.
I am not joking today—this is a public pharmacology lesson for everyone to stay away from drugs!
Reject the temptation of drugs! You think it's just harmless cough syrup? It is "Nitazenes"!
It is hundreds of times stronger than the medical anesthetics used in surgeries!
You think it's just a harmless sweet candy? It is a disguised chemical demon!
Never believe the lies and bullshit of drug dealers! Government strictly bans it for a reason!
Hey you, pretty boys and girls, stop showing off! Chasing vanity and cheap thrills? It's all a fake illusion!
People, wake up! Fight against drugs! We will never compromise!

【Verse 2: The Clinical Reality, The Microgram Micro-Line】
Everyone knows you must sign a consent form before anesthesia in an operating room.
Because the dose of a professional medical drug must be calculated down to the exact microgram!
One drop too many, your breathing stops instantly. One drop too less, the pain drives you insane!
The anesthesiologist stares at your heart rate and oxygen, fighting death with a lifetime of expertise.
Listen to me! Without a professional doctor present, blindly touching drugs can kill you on the spot!
This anti-drug song is here to completely shatter all illusions of chemical abuse!

【Chorus: Declare War on Drugs, Take Back Control】
STAY OFF DRUGS! STAY OFF DRUGS! JUST STAY OFF DRUGS!
Look at those street zombies in the West—don't be a blind fool! Don't be a stupid coward!
Too proud to admit it? Playing brave? Do you really want to drag your own life into absolute misery?
You naive soul, stop putting yourself on an operating table without a doctor!
There is no IV bag, no ventilator, and absolutely nobody watching over you.
Say a loud NO to drugs! Take back the absolute control of your own life right now!

【Bridge: Powerful Contrast, Protecting the Next Generation】
Get this straight! A speck of chemical weight like a few grains of salt can shut down your lungs forever!
In a hospital, it takes a team of ten professionals to drag you back from the grave.
You’re betting your life on a car with no brakes—that’s not bravery, that’s blind ignorance! That’s being a fool!
The line between medicine and poison is thinner than a razor blade. Rejecting drugs is the only truth!
People of Taiwan, stand up! This is a sacred revolution to protect our health!

【Outro: Strict Warning, Warm Salvation】
Parents, see clearly the extreme danger our next generation is facing!
STAY OFF DRUGS! STAY OFF DRUGS! JUST STAY OFF DRUGS!
Look at those street zombies in the West—don't be blind, don't be a fool!
Warn them strictly, declare it out loud, everyone stand up together—
STAY OFF DRUGS! STAY OFF DRUGS! JUST STAY OFF DRUGS!
Stop playing your own anesthesiologist! Wake up, sober up, and return to the right path!
Keep your life. Walk out of this toxic fog. There are people who truly love you, waiting for you to come home...
STAY OFF DRUGS! CHERISH LIFE! JUST STAY OFF DRUGS!

